\c 11
\s Vanhu vanoratidzwa pavangagara
\p
\v 1 Zvino machinda avanhu akagara Jerusaremu; vamwe vanhu vakakanda mijenyawo kuti mumwe pagumi rimwe nerimwe agare Jerusaremu,iro guta dzvene, asi vamwe vapfumbamwe panamamwe maguta.
\v 2 Vanhu vakarumbidza varume vose vakatenda nomoyo wavo kugara Jerusaremu.
\v 3 Zvino ndivo vakuru vorutivi rwenyika vakanga vagere Jerusaremu; asi pamaguta aJudha mumwe nomumwe akagara panzvimbo yake pamaguta avo, ivo vaIsiraeri, navapristi, navaRevhi, navaNetinimi, navana vavaranda vaSoromoni.
\p
\v 4 PaJerusaremu ndipo pakagara vamwe vavana vaJudha, navavana vaBhenjamini. Vana vaJudha ava: Ataya, mwanakomana waUziya, mwanakomana waZekariya, mwanakomana waAmaria, mwanakomana waShefatia, mwanakomana waMaharareri wavana vaPerezi;
\v 5 naMaaseya, mwanakomana waBharuki, mwanakomana waKorihoze, mwanakomana waHazaya, mwanakomana waAdhaya, mwanakomana waJoyaribhi, mwanakomana waZekariya, mwanakomana womuShironi.
\p
\v 6 Vanakomana vose vaPerezi vakanga vagere Jerusaremu vakasvika mazana mana namakumi matanhatu navasere, varume voumhare.
\p
\v 7 Ava ndivo vanakomana vaBhenjamini: Saru mwanakomana waMeshurami, mwanakomana waJoedhi, mwanakomana waPedhaya, mwanakomana waKoraya, mwanakomana waMaaseya, mwanakomana waItieri, mwanakomana waJeshaya.
\v 8 Tevere Gabhai, naSarai, mazana mapfumbamwe namakumi maviri navasere,
\v 9 naJoeri, mwanakomana waZikiri akanga ari mutariri wavo, naJudha, mwanakomana waHasenua, mutariri wechipiri paguta.
\p
\v 10 Vavapristi: Jedhaya, mwanakomana waJoyaribhi, naJakini,
\v 11 Seraya, mwanakomana waHirikia, mwanakomana waMeshurami, mwanakomana waZadhoki, mwanakomana waMerayoti, mwanakomana waAhitubhi, mubati weimba yaMwari,
\v 12 nehama dzavo dzaibata mabasa paimba iyo, vakasvika mazana masere namakumi maviri navaviri; naAdhaya, mwanakomana waJerohami, mwanakomana waPeraira, mwanakomana waAmizi, mwanakomana waZekariya, mwanakomana waPashuri, mwanakomana waMarikija,
\v 13 nehama dzake, vakuru vedzimba dzamadzibaba, mazana maviri namakumi mana navaviri; naAmashi, mwanakomana waAzareri, mwanakomana waAzai, mwanakomana waMeshiremoti, mwanakomana waImeri,
\p
\v 14 nehama dzavo, varume vane simba noumhare, zana namakumi maviri navasere; mutariri wavo akanga ari Zabhidhieri, mwanakomana waHagedhorimi.
\p
\v 15 Uye vaRevhi: Shemaya mwanakomana waHashubhi, mwanakomana waAzirikami, mwanakomana waHashabhia, mwanakomana waBhuni;
\v 16 naShabhetai naJozabhadhi, vavakuru vavaRevhi, vaitarira mabasa okunze eimba yaMwari;
\v 17 naMatania, mwanakomana waMika, mwanakomana waZabhidhi, mwanakomana waAsafi, iye mukuru akatanga kuvonga pakunyengetera, naBhakibhukia, mukuru wechipiri pakati pehama dzake; naAbhidha, mwanakomana waShamua, mwanakomana waGarari, mwanakomana waJedhutuni.
\v 18 VaRevhi vose paguta dzvene vakanga vana mazana maviri namakumi masere navana.
\p
\v 19 Uye varindi vemikova, Akubhi, naTarimoni, nehama dzavo, vairinda pamikova, vakanga vane zana rimwe namakumi manomwe navaviri.
\v 20 Vamwe vakasara vavaIsiraeri, vavapristi navaRevhi vakagara pamaguta ose aJudha; mumwe nomumwe panhaka yake.
\v 21 Asi vaNetinimi vakagara paOferi; Ziha naGishipa vakanga vari vatariri vavaNetinimi.
\p
\v 22 Mutaririwo wavaRevhi paJerusaremu akanga ari Uzi, mwanakomana waBhani, mwanakomana waHashabhia, mwanakomana waMatania, mwanakomana waMika, vavanakomana vaAsafi, ivo vaimbi vaitarira basa reimba yaMwari.
\v 23 nekuti mambo akanga araira pamusoro pavo, navaimbi vaipiwa mubayiro wakatarwa zuva rimwe nerimwe.
\p
\v 24 Petahia, mwanakomana waMeshazabheri, wavana vaZera, mwanakomana waJudha, ndiye akanga ari mubatsiri wamambo pamashoko ose avanhu.
\p
\v 25 Kana iri misha nokuruwa rwayo, vamwe vavana vaJudha vakagara paKiriatiarabha nemisha yaro, napaDhibhoni nemisha yaro, napaJekabhizeeri nemisha yaro;
\v 26 napaJeshua, napaMoradha, napaBheerishebha nemisha yawo;
\v 27 napaHazarishuari, napaBheerishebha nemisha yawo;
\v 28 napaZikiragi, napaMekona nemisha yawo;
\v 29 napaEnirimoni, napaZora, napaJarimuti;
\v 30 neZanowa, neAdhurami, nemisha yawo, neRakishi noruwa rwaro, neAzeka nemisha yaro. Naizvozvo vakavaka misasa yavo kubva paBheerishebha kusvikira pamupata weHinomi.
\v 31 Vana vaBhenjamini vakagara kubva paGebha, paMikimashi, neAya, napaBhetieri nemisha yawo;
\v 32 neAnatoti, neNobhi, neAnania;
\v 33 neHazori, neRama, neGitaimi;
\v 34 neHadhidhi, neZebhoimi, neNebharati;
\v 35 neRodhi, neOno, neGehaharashimi.
\v 36 Vamwe vaRevhi vamapoka aJudha vakagara pakati pavaBhenjamini.
